# FOOD-LABELS - Storage Protocol Version 0.1.0(Proposal)

DESCRIPTION
  Standards for labeling and storing food items at Hive Helsinki

PROCEDURES
  1. LABEL REQUIREMENTS
      - intra name clearly written or communal clearly written
      - Date of storage clearly written

  2. DURATION RULES
      - One day storage recommended
      - Multi-day items extra clearly marked as communal, or personal (beverages for coffee or tea, condiments, non-fridge items)
      - No long-term storage

COMMON ERRORS
  - Unclear handwriting
  - Missing dates
  - Missing names
  - Unmarked containers
  - Fridge full of milk or condiments
  - So many cartons of milk

SEE ALSO
  kitchen(1), fridge-deep-clean(1)
